It's so nice having a reliable, affordable 24-hour Jamaican go-to spot within walking distance! Take-out only, credit and debit cards ok. Tasty. $6 small container of rice and peas, brown stew chicken and side of boiled cabbage fills me right up and then some. Standard Jamaican options include jerk and curry chicken, oxtail, goat, fish. Soup, patties and dumplings also available. Patties seem to go fast early in the day. Can be a line around lunch and dinner times, or even late evening, say 11p or midnight. Not much room to wait inside. Be sure to tip the server/cashier!
